            <h3>Wemanity Group (METRO France)</h3>
            <p class="experience-meta">Fullstack Developer | March 2022 - March 2024</p>
            <p>Worked as a Fullstack Developer using Node.js, React.js, TypeScript and GraphQL.</p>
